{"tid":142071,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友阿媽叫我上去食飯  我拒絕左","createTime":"2017-03-03T12:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T15:20:20.000Z","uid":24249,"like":0,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dceff6259d468b2ee11485c4a493ff54667b4a7","tid":142071,"uid":24249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"今日女朋友細妹生日，咁佢有叫男朋友上去食飯。咁佢阿媽叫埋我上去喎(雖然之前有去過)但身為毒撚，我又驚又怕羞。之後係電話入面聽到......<br />\n女朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    佢阿媽=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：又唔黎呀？！(事關之前已經拒絕過同埋話下次一定去)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：係囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 你男朋友咁高逗,睇下你,唔值錢架啦你<br />\n我係電話到講:唔係，我低賤先啱<br />\n<br />\n之後女朋友就因為我唔上去食飯&amp;雙重標準(事關我屋企人生日我都有叫佢嚟食飯,佢都會嚟，但佢屋企人生日我唔去)而嬲我<br />\n<br />\n想問應該點樣拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244e24351c4874fa609f2bd06e50306d0100c863","tid":142071,"uid":24249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咗"},{"pid":"7d9e564947c0b5b612614d98ce2bf8e4f134304f","tid":142071,"uid":24249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed31348d2e2b3aba77ab085dcc2c5f0af958d76c","tid":142071,"uid":52831,"like":0,"dislike